ssing. Further, it provides its cloud-communication services to clients in the banking and financial, aviation, retail, e-commerce, logistics, healthcare, hospitality, media and entertainment, pharmaceutical, and telecom sectors. The company was incorporated in 2004 and is headquartered in Mumbai, India. Route Mobile Limited is a subsidiary of Proximus Global SA."}}